name: Flounder
text:
Support (Whenever this character quests, you may add their {S} to another chosen character's {S} this turn.)
I'M NOT A GUPPY If you have a character named Ariel in play, you pay 1 {I} less to play this character.
flavor_text: "Ariel, Ariel! You won't believe what I found!"

name: Hades
flavor_text: "On this cute little plot Ursula tentacles are sold a mile away. That sneaky sea witch… Wait! I can use this thing. While you keep those hateful Illumineers busy, I can carry out my plan."

name: Hans
text: ROYAL SCHEMES When you play this character, if a Princess or Queen character is in play, gain 1 lore.
flavor_text: Hans was confident he could bring Anna to Ursula-all he needed was something of Kristoff's to lure her in.

name: Iduna
text: ENDURING LOVE When this character is banished, you may put this card into your inkwell facedown and exerted.
flavor_text:
"Come my darling, homeward bound
When all is lost, then all is found."

name: John Silver
flavor_text: "There are strange things on the edge of the map: sea witches, entangled glimmers, and so on. I'll stick with my ship, thank you very much."

name: Olaf
text:
Shift: Discard an item card (You may discard an item card to play this on top of one of your characters named Olaf.)
CARROTS ALL AROUND! Whenever he quests, each of your other characters gets +{S} equal to this character's {S} this turn.

name: Olaf
text: Support (Whenever this character quests, you may add their {S} to another chosen character's {S} this turn.)
flavor_text: "Isn't this Kristoff's hat? If he went this way, he'll be caught in that storm!"

name: Pascal
text: COLORFUL TACTICS When you play this character, look at the top 3 cards of your deck and put them back in any order.
flavor_text: If you want to find something hidden, get someone who's an expert at hiding.

name: Prince Phillip
text:
Support (Whenever this character quests, you may add their {S} to another chosen character's {S} this turn.)
BEST DEFENSE Whenever one of your characters is chosen for Support, they gain Resist +1 this turn. (Damage dealt to them is reduced by 1.)

name: Rapunzel
text: PERCEPTIVE PARTNER While you have a character named Pascal in play, this character gains Ward. (Opponents can't choose them except to challenge.)
flavor_text: "Pascal! A new flower for the wall!"

name: Scuttle
text: LET ME SEE When you play this character, look at the top 4 cards of your deck. You may reveal an item card and put it into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.
flavor_text: "Wow. This is special. This is very, very unusual."

name: Sisu
flavor_text: "It may feel impossible, but sometimes, you just have to take the first step, even before you're ready."

name: The Queen
text: CONSULT THE SPELLBOOK {E} — Look at the top 4 cards of your deck. You may reveal an item card and put it into your hand. If that item costs 3 or less, you may play it for free instead and it enters play exerted. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

name: Transformed Chef
text: A CULINARY MASTERPIECE When you play this character, remove up to 2 damage from chosen character.
flavor_text:
"A good, hot meal will set you right as rain."
- Mrs. Potts

name: Triton
text:
Shift 6 (You may pay 6 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Triton.)
IMPOSING PRESENCE Opposing characters get -1 {S} for each location you have in play.

name: Triton
text: CONSIGN TO THE DEPTHS {E}, Banish one of your items — Gain 3 lore.
flavor_text: "If this is the only way, so be it."

name: Triton
text:
SUPERIOR SWIMMER During your turn, this character gains Evasive. (They can challenge characters with Evasive.)
KEEPER OF ATLANTICA Whenever one of your locations is banished, you may put that card into your inkwell facedown and exerted.

name: Tuk Tuk
flavor_text:
"Some say he's easily distracted. They're not wrong..."
-Raya

name: Dig a Little Deeper
text:
Sing Together 8 (Any number of your or your teammates' characters with total cost 8 or more may {E} to sing this song for free.)
Look at the top 7 cards of your deck. Put 2 into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

name: Glean
text: Banish chosen item. Its player gains 2 lore.
flavor_text: "Maybe this is just what I need to make my invention work."

name: Seldom All They Seem
text:
(A character with cost 2 or more can {E} to sing this song for free.)
Chosen character gets -3 {S} this turn.
flavor_text:
I know you
I walked with you once upon a dream

name: Treasures Untold
text:
(A character with cost 6 or more can {E} to sing this song for free.)
Return up to 2 item cards from your discard into your hand.
flavor_text: How many wonders can one cavern hold?

name: Field of Ice
text: ICY DEFENSE Whenever you play a character, they gain Resist +1 until the start of your next turn. (Damage dealt to them is reduced by 1.)

name: Great Stone Dragon
text:
ASLEEP This item enters play exerted.
AWAKEN {E} — Put a character card from your discard into your inkwell facedown and exerted.

name: Ice Block
text: CHILLY LABOR {E} — Chosen character gets -1 {S} this turn.
flavor_text: Frozen ink can be harvested and processed to many useful ends.

name: Ariel’s Grotto
text: TREASURE TROVE While you have 3 or more items in play, this location gets +2 {L}.

name: Winter Camp
text: HELP THE WOUNDED Whenever a character quests while here, remove up to 2 damage from them. If they're a Hero character, remove up to 4 damage instead.

name: Aladdin
text:
Shift: Discard a location card (You may discard a location card to play this on top of one of your characters named Aladdin.)
CRASHING THROUGH Whenever this character quests, you may banish chosen item.

name: Aladdin
flavor_text: "How about we get straight to the part where I leave quickly and you scream after me? No? I can't say I didn't give you a chance."

name: Arges
flavor_text:
"Looks like you got some big feelings there, buddy—let's stomp 'em out!"
-Hades

name: Ariel
text: I WANT MORE Whenever you play a song, you may draw a card, then choose and discard a card.
flavor_text: Everything she's ever wanted is almost in reach.

name: Ariel
text:
Shift 4 (You may pay 4 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Ariel.)
AMPLIFIED VOICE Whenever you play a song, you may pay 2 {I} to deal 3 damage to chosen character.

name: Beast
text: Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
flavor_text: He's even tougher than he looks.

name: Chi-Fu
text: OVERLY CAUTIOUS While this character has no damage, he gets +2 {L}.
flavor_text: "You, there! Keep that fighting away from here! It is imperative that I write to the Emperor."

name: Chien-Po
text: Bodyguard (This character may enter play exerted. An opposing character who challenges one of your characters must choose one with Bodyguard if able.)

name: Donald Duck
text: BOARDING PARTY During your turn, whenever this character banishes a character in a challenge, your other characters get +1 {L} this turn.
flavor_text: Nobody stands a chance against the daring duck of the high seas!

name: Hercules
text:
Bodyguard (This character may enter play exerted. An opposing character who challenges one of your characters must choose one with Bodyguard if able.)
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)

name: LeFou
text: I LEARNED FROM THE BEST During your turn, you may play this character for free if an opposing character was banished in a challenge this turn.

name: Li Shang
flavor_text: Immovable as a mountain and fierce as a dragon—the Empire's finest warrior.

name: Ling
text: FULL OF SPIRIT Your Hero characters get +1 {S}.
flavor_text: A good friend is handy in a fight.

name: Luisa Madrigal
text: I'M THE STRONG ONE While you have another character in play, this character gets +2 {S}.
flavor_text: There's no way Ursula's creatures are getting to that donkey.

name: Magic Broom
text: WINGED FOR A DAY During your turn, this character gains Evasive. (They can challenge characters with Evasive.)
flavor_text: It spends its days keeping the treasured glimmers in the Hall of Lorcana sparkling clean.

name: Magic Broom
text:
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
ARMY OF BROOMS This character gets +2 {S} for each other character named Magic Broom you have in play.

name: Mickey Mouse
text:
Shift 3 (You may pay 3 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Mickey Mouse.)
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
SWEEP AWAY When you play this character, deal damage to chosen character equal to the number of Broom characters you have in play.

name: Mickey Mouse
text: STAND STRONG When you play this character, chosen character gains Challenger +2 this turn. (They get +2 {S} while challenging.)
flavor_text: He sets the standard for intrepid adventurers everywhere.

name: Mulan
flavor_text: "Maybe what I really wanted was to prove I could do things right, so when I looked in the mirror, I'd see someone worthwhile."

name: Philoctetes
text:
YOU GOTTA STAY FOCUSED Your Hero characters gain Challenger +1. (They get +1 {S} while challenging.)
SHAMELESS PROMOTER Whenever you play a Hero character, gain 1 lore.

name: Piglet
text:
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
NOT SO SMALL ANYMORE While you have no cards in your hand, this character can challenge ready characters.

name: Rajah
text: STEADY GAZE While you have no cards in your hand, characters with cost 4 or less can't challenge this character.
flavor_text: As regal as his namesake and just as powerful.

name: Raya
text:
Challenger +2 (While challenging, this character gets +2 {S}.)
Resist +2 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 2.)
YOU GAVE IT YOUR BEST During your turn, whenever this character banishes another character in a challenge, you may draw a card.

name: Yao
text: Challenger +2 (While challenging, this character gets +2 {S}.)
flavor_text: "I'm gonna hit you so hard, it'll make your ancestors dizzy."

name: Avalanche
text: Deal 1 damage to each opposing character. You may banish chosen location.
flavor_text: A little snow never hurt anyone. That big rock, however...

name: I Find ’Em, I Flatten ’Em
text:
(A character with cost 4 or more can {E} to sing this song for free.)
Banish all items.
flavor_text: All the most difficult missions are for me, because I am indestructible.

name: One Last Hope
text:
(A character with cost 3 or more can {E} to sing this song for free.)
Chosen character gains Resist +2 until the start of your next turn. If a Hero character is chosen, they may also challenge ready characters this turn. (Damage dealt to them is reduced by 2.)

name: The Mob Song
text:
Sing Together 10 (Any number of your or your teammates' characters with total cost 10 or more may {E} to sing this song for free.)
Deal 3 damage to up to 3 chosen characters and/or locations.

name: Triton's Decree
text: Each opponent chooses one of their characters and deals 2 damage to them.
flavor_text: "Ursula's foul creatures are not welcome in my kingdom!"

name: Fortisphere
text:
RESOURCEFUL When you play this item, you may draw a card.
EXTRACT OF STEEL 1 {I}, Banish this item — Chosen character of yours gains Bodyguard until the start of your next turn. (An opposing character who challenges one of your characters must choose one with Bodyguard if able.)

name: Imperial Bow
text: WITHIN RANGE {E}, 1 {I} — Chosen Hero character gains Challenger +2 and Evasive this turn. (They get +2 {S} while challenging. They can challenge characters with Evasive.)

name: RLS Legacy's Cannon
text: BA-BOOM! {E}, 2 {I}, Discard a card — Deal 2 damage to chosen character or location.
flavor_text:
"So help me, I'll use the ship's cannons to blast ya all to kingdom come!"
- John Silver

name: The Wall
text: PROTECT THE REALM While you have an exerted character here, your other locations can't be challenged.

name: Thebes
text: IF YOU CAN MAKE IT HERE... During your turn, whenever a character banishes another character in a challenge while here, gain 2 lore.

name: Cinderella
text:
Singer 9 (This character counts as cost 9 to sing songs.)
BEAUTIFUL VOICE Whenever this character sings a song, your other Princess characters get +1 {L} this turn.

name: Minnie Mouse
text:
Bodyguard (This character may enter play exerted. An opposing character who challenges one of your characters must choose one with Bodyguard if able.)
DRAMATIC ENTRANCE When you play this character, banish chosen opposing character with 5 {S} or more.

name: Look at This Family
text:
Sing Together 7 (Any number of your or your teammates' characters with total cost 7 or more may {E} to sing this song for free.)
Look at the top 5 cards of your deck. You may reveal up to 2 character cards and put them into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

name: Ursula
text:
Shift 5 (You may pay 5 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Ursula.)
NOW I AM THE RULER! Whenever this character quests, exert chosen character.
YOU'LL LISTEN TO ME! Other characters can't exert to sing songs.

name: Yen Sid
text:
TIMELY INTERVENTION When you play this character, if you have a character named Magic Broom in play, you may draw a card.
ARCANE STUDY While you have 2 or more Broom characters in play, this character gets +2 {L}.

name: Second Star to the Right
text:
Sing Together 10 (Any number of your or your teammates' characters with total cost 10 or more may {E} to sing this song for free.)
Chosen player draws 5 cards.

name: Diablo
text:
Shift: Discard an action card (You may discard an action card to play this on top of one of your characters named Diablo.)
Evasive (Only characters with Evasive can challenge this character.)
CIRCLE FAR AND WIDE During each opponent's turn, whenever they draw a card while this character is exerted, you may draw a card.

name: Jasmine
text: CUNNING MANEUVER When you play this character and whenever she's challenged, each opponent chooses and discards a card.

name: We Don't Talk About Bruno
text:
(A character with cost 5 or more can {E} to sing this song for free.)
Return chosen character to their player's hand, then that player discards a card at random.

name: Goofy
text:
Rush (This character can challenge the turn they're played.)
SUPER PEANUT POWERS Whenever this character challenges another character, gain 2 lore.

name: Sisu
text:
Shift 6 (You may pay 6 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Sisu.)
I GOT THIS! When you play this character, banish all opposing characters with 2 {S} or less.

name: Snuggly Duckling
text: ROUTINE RUCKUS Whenever a character with 3 {S} or more challenges another character while here, gain 1 lore. If the challenging character has 6 {S} or more, gain 3 lore instead.

name: Anna
text: LET ME HELP YOU Whenever this character quests, your other Hero characters get +1 {L} this turn.

name: The Queen
text: CONSULT THE SPELLBOOK {E} — Look at the top 4 cards of your deck. You may reveal an item card and put it into your hand. If that item costs 3 or less, you may play it for free instead and it enters play exerted. Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

name: Ariel’s Grotto
text: TREASURE TROVE While you have 3 or more items in play, this location gets +2 {L}.

name: Ariel
text:
Shift 4 (You may pay 4 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Ariel.)
AMPLIFIED VOICE Whenever you play a song, you may pay 2 {I} to deal 3 damage to chosen character.

name: Piglet
text:
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
NOT SO SMALL ANYMORE While you have no cards in your hand, this character can challenge ready characters.

name: The Wall
text: PROTECT THE REALM While you have an exerted character here, your other locations can't be challenged.

name: Yen Sid
text:
TIMELY INTERVENTION When you play this character, if you have a character named Magic Broom in play, you may draw a card.
ARCANE STUDY While you have 2 or more Broom characters in play, this character gets +2 {L}.

name: Mulan
text:
Shift 5 (You may pay 5 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Mulan.)
STRAIGHT SHOOTER When you play this character, if you used Shift to play her, she gets +3 {S} this turn.
TRIPLE SHOT During your turn, whenever this character deals damage to another character in a challenge, deal the same amount of damage to up to 2 other chosen characters.

name: Mickey Mouse
text:
Shift 3 (You may pay 3 {I} to play this on top of one of your characters named Mickey Mouse.)
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is reduced by 1.)
SWEEP AWAY When you play this character, deal damage to chosen character equal to the number of Broom characters you have in play.
